'''Paladins''' are found in [[East Ardougne]], wandering near the castle and market. They are from Ardougne's Holy Order of Paladins, and wear the symbol of [[Saradomin]]. Three paladins are found in the [[Underground Pass (dungeon)|Underground Pass]] and must be killed during the [[Underground Pass|quest]]. They have special drops related to the quest.

Players can [[pickpocket]] paladins at level 70 [[Thieving]] to gain 151.8 [[experience]], 80 [[coins]] and 2 [[chaos rune]]s. The success rate of pick pocketing paladins has been estimated to be 10/17 at level 99 without any modifiers.

