==Combat==
Not many people train [[Combat]] on paladins, as they have mediocre drops (the most notable being [[Clue scroll (medium)|medium clue scrolls]]), and because they can hit up to 8 [[hitpoints]], and often do.

Paladins will attack players that they catch trying to steal from the [[silver stall]], [[Ardougne Gem Stall.|gem stall]], and [[Ardougne Spice Stall.|spice stall]], but will, if nearby, also attack a player if they attempt to talk to the owner of a stall recently stolen from by the respective player.

A good strategy when training on paladins is by using [[Protect from Melee]] then restoring your prayer points by the nearby [[altar]]. Keep repeating the process to prevent any excessive health loss. Healing using food stolen from nearby stalls is also an alternative.

Paladins are weak to [[Magic]] and Crush attacks.

